attributionInfo.agentName: Monica Breckenridge ABR CDPE CLHMS GRI MRP PSA RSPS SFR SRES

data.description: Welcome to this large, spacious 5 bed 3 bath home in the very sought after Lorson Ranch neighborhood. This home is located within 10 minutes of Fort Carson. It is also very close to Peterson SFB and Schriever AFB and has NO HOA DUES! The main level has vaulted ceilings, a large kitchen, breakfast bar and living room that is open concept. Three bedrooms, including the master bedroom, are located on the main level. In the large finished basement you will find an additional two bedrooms and an additional bathroom. There is plenty of room for entertaining both on the main level and in the basement. There is also an enormous amount of storage space in this home. The Central heat and air will keep you cool in the summer and nice and toasty in the winter. The hot water heater is brand new and was just installed in September, 2023.  This home has been well cared for and is ready for its next family that can call it home for years to come.
